{"word":"G4008 - πέραν - péran - per'-an - Beyond","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">πέραν</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">péran</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">per'-an</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Beyond</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adverb / வினையடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"அப்புறம், அக்கரை - வினையடை"},{"paragraph":"further, beyond, besides"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Apparently the accusative case of an obsolete derivation of <b>&#x03C0;&#x03B5;&#x03B9;&#x0301;&#x03C1;&#x03C9;</b> <b>peiro&#x0304;</b> (to &ldquo;peirce&rdquo;); <i>through</i> (as adverb or preposition), that is, <i>across:</i> - beyond, farther (other) side, over.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}